dji.sdk.api

Class DJIError

  • java.lang.Object
    • dji.sdk.api.DJIError

  • public class DJIError
extends java.lang.Object

    DJI Error Define Class

    If you want to find out the classification of error for dealing with exceptions, DJIError class may provide a convenient way to handle this situation. DJIError defines all types of error which may occur in any time of the flight. On a basis of the error, you could design a corresponding strategy for maintaining status of drone.
    Version:
    V2.1.0
    Author:
    DJI Software
